			a#history
			.large-6.medium-12.small-12.columns
				h2 History
				p At Burning Man 2016 we will take on our new identity, #[em Hotel California] - in past years we have been the #[em Church of the Fifth Element] (2015), #[em Home Sweet Dome] (2014) and before that, #[em Burners on the Fence] (2013) and #[em Camp Bikini Bottoms] (earlier). Our community is dedicated to making our camp the most hospitable piece of land on the Playa, offering first-rate amenities to all visitors. 

				p Everyone is #[strong radically welcome] to Hotel California. Members in the past years came from everywhere in the US, Germany, France, India, Australia... Members in the past have been super cool, super weird, sometimes assholes, most of the time really awesome – the point is, we don’t discriminate. We welcome strangers and newbies – anyone can play with us.
				
