			.large-6.medium-12.small-12.columns
				h2 Art
				p Come check out our art installation, an eight-foot-wide fire pit made out of stainless steel -  the biggest fire pit on the playa.

				p We built the fire pit last year and used it every day during the burn. We used #[strong TONS] of wood, and many people enjoyed the beauty of the flames for hours at a time. We want to do it again this year! However, due to the insane amount of heat applied to the structure, we have some work to do: the base (holding the wood at the bottom of the firepit) needs to be rebuilt; we also need to repair many of the welds holding the panels together.

				p If you feel generous and would like to contribute to our project, please use the donate button below and give what you can!

